Fixed: `refine-drafts.ps1` will no longer save Copilot CLI log/footer text into refined draft files.

The change is in `coworker/scripts/workers/gh-copilot.ps1`: when `Invoke-GHCopilot` runs in `-CaptureOutput` mode, it now adds `--silent` automatically, so capture-based callers receive only the model response. That keeps the fix scoped to scripted output capture and leaves normal console runs unchanged. I also appended the required task note to `D:\workspace\Browser4Team\coworker\tasks\300logs\2026\04\06\MEMORY.20260406.md` and backfilled the April monthly rollup in `D:\workspace\Browser4Team\coworker\tasks\300logs\2026\04\MEMORY.202604.md` with the missing 2026-04-05 summary.


